{"article_id":"FOIhxxBNy5q0WmMP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Saturday defended his administration ' s hurricane recovery effort in Puerto Rico","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"and questioned the leadership of San Juan Mayor Carmen Yulin Cruz","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"who is criticizing the president 's effort","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"to get supplies , electricity and other relief to the U.S. island .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"after facing criticism over his attacks of the mayor ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Trump tweeted praise for several other officials","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"involved in the recovery ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"including the governors of Puerto Rico and the Virgin Islands .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"He also praised Puerto ' s Rico ' s representative in Congress .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"`` We must all be united","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"in offering assistance to everyone","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"suffering in Puerto Rico and elsewhere in the wake of this terrible disaster , ''","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"the president tweeted .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"\" The Governor of Puerto Rico , Ricardo Rossello , is a great guy and leader","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"who is really working hard , \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"\" Thank you Ricky ! \"","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"\" Just spoke to Governor Kenneth Mapp of the U.S. Virgin Islands","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"who stated","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"that # FEMA and Military are doing a GREAT job !","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Thank you Governor ! \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"the president said .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"He also tweeted :","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"\" Congresswoman Jennifer Gonzalez-Colon of Puerto Rico has been wonderful to deal with","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"and a great representative of the people .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Thank you ! \"","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Earlier Saturday , the president singled out Cruz for criticism ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"accusing her of `` poor leadership . ''","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"\" Such poor leadership ability by the Mayor of San Juan , and others in Puerto Rico ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"who are not able to get their workers to help , \"","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Trump said in a series of tweets .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"`` They want everything to be done for them","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"when it should be a community effort .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"10,000 Federal workers now on Island","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"doing a fantastic job . \"","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"He also tweeted :","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"`` Results of recovery efforts will speak much louder than complaints by San Juan Mayor .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Doing everything","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"we can","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"to help great people of PR ! ''","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Cruz , in response , said later Saturday morning","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that she ' ll \" continue to do whatever I have to do \"","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"to get federal hurricane assistance .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"\" I will continue to do whatever I have to do ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"say whatever I have to say ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"compliment the people","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"I need to compliment","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"and call out the people","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"I need to call out , \"","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"she told MSNBC .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"\" I am not going to be distracted by small comments , by politics , by petty issues .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"This is one goal","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"and it 's to save lives . \"","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Cruz also argued","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"that Lt. General Jeffrey Buchanan ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"appointed Thursday","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"to lead the administration ' s response on the U.S. island ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"says","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"he will need more troops and equipment .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"\" So , who am I ? \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"she asked .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"\" I 'm just a little mayor from the capital city of San Juan .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"This is a three star general","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"telling the world right now","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"he does not have the appropriate means and tools","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"to take care of the situation . \"","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"Trump also tweeted Saturday :","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"\" The Mayor of San Juan ,","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"who was very complimentary only a few days ago ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"has now been told by the Democrats","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"that you must be nasty to Trump . \"","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"Trump pledged Friday to spare no effort","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"to help Puerto Ricans recover from Hurricane Maria 's ruinous aftermath","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"even as Cruz accused the administration of `` killing us with the inefficiency . ''","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Cruz said later Friday","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that she wanted to `` make sure","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"somebody is in charge","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that is up to the task","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"of saving lives , ''","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"while the president asserted","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that U.S. officials and emergency personnel are working all-out against daunting odds , with `` incredible '' results .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Trump also tweeted :","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"\" The military and first responders ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"despite no electric , roads , phones etc. ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"have done an amazing job .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Puerto Rico was totally destroyed , ''","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"and , `` Fake News CNN and NBC are going out of their way","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"to disparage our great First Responders as a way","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"to `` get Trump . '","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"' Not fair to FR or effort ! ''","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Among the first","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"to criticize Trump 's tweets Saturday","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"was Broadway actor and `` Hamilton '' creator Lin-Manuel Miranda .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"`` You 're going straight to hell , @ realDonaldTrump , ''","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Miranda , a multi-million-dollar Hillary Clinton fundraiser , tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"Hillary Clinton , the 2016 Democratic nominee , tweeted her support for Cruz .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"`` Don ' t let anyone make you feel alone , ''","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"`` We are with you and Puerto Rico . ''","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"Puerto Rico Gov . Ricardo Rossello , a Democrat , has said","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"the administration is being responsive to the island 's needs","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"and on Saturday appeared to try to deflect questions about Cruz 's comments .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"He suggested","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"the Trump-Cruz issue was to his `` side ''","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"his message is that he 's `` here","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"to help ''","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and collaborate with the federal government on resources .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"On Friday , Rossello said","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"Trump has responded to his requests","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"after the island was clipped by Hurricane Irma ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"then struck by Maria .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"He also said","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"the Federal Emergency Management Agency and its director , Brock Long , have essentially been in contact with him `` all of the time .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"Trump 's acting homeland security secretary , Elaine Duke , visited the island Friday ,","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"surveying the landscape by helicopter in an hour-long tour ,","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"driving past still-flooded streets , twisted billboards and roofs with gaping holes ,","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"and offering encouragement to some of the 10,000 emergency personnel","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"she says","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"the U.S. government has on the ground .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"On Thursday , the U.S. military named Buchanan","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"to oversee the response effort .","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"Duke tried , too , to move on from the remarks","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"she made a day earlier","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"in which she called the federal relief effort a `` good-news story . ''","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"But on that front , she ran into winds as fierce as Maria .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"`` We are dying ,","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"and you are killing us with the inefficiency , ''","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"Cruz said in a news conference .","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"`` I am begging ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"begging anyone","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"that can hear us ,","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"to save us from dying . ''","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"Thousands more Puerto Ricans got water and rationed food Friday","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"as an aid bottleneck began to ease .","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"By now , telecommunications are back for about 30 percent of the island ,","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"nearly half of the supermarkets have reopened at least for reduced hours","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"and about 60 percent of the gas stations are pumping .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"But many remain desperate for necessities , most urgently water , long after the Sept. 20 hurricane .","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"Puerto Rico is `` totally unable '' to handle the catastrophe on its own .","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"`` They are working so hard ,","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"but there 's nothing left , ''","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"`` It 's been wiped out . ''","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"the government is `` fully engaged in the disaster and the response and recovery effort . ''","depth":7},{"id":148,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"he was not aware of Duke 's `` good-news '' remark .","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"`` I have n't heard what she said , ''","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"`` I can tell you this :","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"We have done an incredible job","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"considering there 's absolutely nothing","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"to work with . ''","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"Yet","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"even in voicing solidarity and sympathy with Puerto Rico ,","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"he drew attention again to the island 's pre-hurricane debt burden and infrastructure woes ,","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"leaving doubt how far Washington will go","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"to make the U.S. territory whole .","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"`` Ultimately the government of Puerto Rico will have to work with us","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"to determine how this massive rebuilding effort","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"-- it will end up being one of the biggest ever --","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"will be funded and organized ,","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"and what we will do with the tremendous amount of existing debt already on the island , ''","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"`` We will not rest , however ,","depth":8},{"id":168,"text":"until the people of Puerto Rico are safe . ''","depth":8},{"id":169,"text":"Earlier he tweeted :","depth":8},{"id":170,"text":"`` The fact is that Puerto Rico has been destroyed by two hurricanes .","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"Big decisions will have to be made as to the cost of its rebuilding ! ''","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"Speaking to the press ,","depth":7},{"id":173,"text":"and taking no questions ,","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"Duke said","depth":7},{"id":175,"text":"neither she nor Trump will rest","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"until displaced Puerto Ricans are back home ,","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"schools , hospitals and clean water are back","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"and the island 's economy is moving again .","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"Duke said","depth":7},{"id":180,"text":"she is aware","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"people are suffering","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"and `` clearly the situation in Puerto Rico after the devastating hurricane is not satisfactory . ''","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"Trump weighed in on his way to New Jersey for the weekend .","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"He praised his emergency management director , Brock Long ,","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"for doing a `` fantastic job , ''","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"pointed out","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"that Duke is serving in an acting capacity","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"`` she 's working very hard . ''","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"Duke said","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"before leaving Washington","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"that the federal relief effort was a `` good-news story ''","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"because of `` our ability","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"to reach people and the limited number of deaths . '' `` Let me clarify , ''","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"she said Friday upon her arrival in San Juan .","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"She said","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"she meant","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"`` it was good news","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"that people of Puerto Rico and many public servants of the United States are working together . ''","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":399,"left":226,"right":398,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":226,"left":203,"right":225,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":203,"left":0,"right":202,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":202,"left":1,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":208,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":207,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":207,"left":4,"right":206,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":206,"left":5,"right":205,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":205,"left":204,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":211,"right":223,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":211,"left":210,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":10,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":214,"right":222,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":214,"left":213,"right":17,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":212,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":218,"right":221,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":218,"left":217,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":216,"right":21,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":1